    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>Instances are useful for duplicating geometry by referencing an original copy to save memory and time when processing and rendering many objects. These instances can then be shaded differently to create interesting and realistic variations without overloading the artist or the computer with many unique copies.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"d6921adc-adc3-4551-a72b-5f88e5b9631a\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>See <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661429\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instancing</a> for more information on instancing.</p></div></div><h2 id=\"Instances-CopytoPointsSOP\">Copy to Points SOP</h2><p>Create a <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://www.sidefx.com/docs/houdini/nodes/sop/copytopoints.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Copy to Points</a> SOP and wire geometry to be instanced into the first input, and positions to instance to in the second input. </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"616\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644181/instance.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=318&amp;height=216\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644181/instance.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"216\" data-width=\"318\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644211\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"instance.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644181\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a29be4bc-3a25-4754-8eb2-1a160da59754\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644181/instance.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=318&amp;height=216 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644181/instance.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=318&amp;height=216 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"Instances-InstanceOBJ\">Instance OBJ</h2><p>Create an <strong>Instance</strong> OBJ as you would normally create <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://www.sidefx.com/docs/houdini/copy/instancing\" rel=\"nofollow\">Houdini instances</a>. </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"616\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644181/instnace1.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=340&amp;height=248\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644181/instnace1.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"248\" data-width=\"340\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644214\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"instnace1.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644181\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a0a9fe20-7e90-4900-ae1b-5b543e298abc\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644181/instnace1.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=340&amp;height=248 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644181/instnace1.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=340&amp;height=248 1x\"></span><p /><p>In the Instance node, set your <strong>Instance object</strong> and select <strong>Fast point instancing</strong> or<strong> Full point instancing</strong>. Currently these two options result in the same behavior in the renderer.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"616\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644181/fastpointinstancing.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433124991&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=460&amp;height=285\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644181/fastpointinstancing.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433124991&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"285\" data-width=\"460\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644205\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"fastpointinstancing.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644181\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a347134e-fb55-4d78-b1f6-afdbe54f5441\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644181/fastpointinstancing.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433124991&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=460&amp;height=285 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644181/fastpointinstancing.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433124991&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=460&amp;height=285 1x\"></span><p /><p>To override material for the instanced objects, we can use the Material SOP inside the Instance. </p>"
    }
